*FOX  YY(2)=YY(2)-C1M7*CUR/CHI*YI/(XI*XI+YI*YI)*(SQRT((LIN+L)*(LIN+L)+
*FOX  XI*XI+YI*YI)-SQRT((LIN-L)*(LIN-L)+XI*XI+YI*YI)) ;
!     A = A-1E-7*2*L*CUR/CHI*XI/(XI*XI+YI*YI)
!     B = B-1E-7*2*L*CUR/CHI*YI/(XI*XI+YI*YI)
!
