!  THE X-AXIS. THE 4-D ELLIPSOID IS GIVEN BY THE BOUNDARY OF A
!  DISTRIBUTION OF PARTICLES WITH MAXIMUM EMITANCE OF MODE I AND II,
!  EUI AND EUII RESPECTIVELY.
!  BINARY PRINT ON FILE 11 OF 22 VALUES :
!  POSITION [M],
